tourBios.curYrHigh: Finished T24 at the Mainland China Qualifying Tournament in early March at Wolong Lake GC in Liuzhou to secure conditionally-exempt playing privileges for the season.
tourBios.carHigh: 2014: Played in 10 PGA TOUR China Series' events, making one cut—at the Hainan Open in November. Finished T60… Fired a final-round, 10-over 81 in severely windy conditions at the OneAsia Tour's Nanshan China Masters in mid-October to T53.
tourBios.personal: Is the younger brother of PGA TOUR China Series' member Xin Jun Zhang.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA Tour China Serie was T60th in 2014 at the Sanya Hainan Open.
